Package: anansi
Type: Package
Title: Consensus and Discrepancy Visualization for Sets of Phylogenetic Networks
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Nicolae", "Sapoval", email = "nick.sapoval@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to visualize sets of explicit reticulate phylogenetic
    networks (extended Newick / 'evonet') over a fixed taxon set in a
    DensiTree-style consensus/discrepancy view. Networks are overlaid on a
    shared tip ordering so that agreement appears dense and conflict appears
    diffuse, with backbone-tree and reticulation-edge signals shown together.
    Supports restricting all networks to a subset of taxa. Built on 'ape',
    'tanggle' and 'ggtree'.
